  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    This is so complicated to document as its been such a varied working life. But working backwards... Over ten years as a software engineer mainly focused in educational software development. Covering various programming
    languages, frameworks, CMS and graphics engines. Experience in WEB design and development. Working with SQL Data Base systems, as well as design, normalization and migration. Also knowledge graphic design tools for image manipulation , User Interfaces design, Web sites, logos and other etc.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ecology and Evolution"
      subtitle="1993 to 1996 at Leeds University, West Yorkshire, UK"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Access to HE"
      subtitle="1992 to 1993 at Joseph Priestly College, Peel Street, Morley"
    />
