    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Engineer, Full stack developer at Research Machines (RM plc)"
      subtitle="From 1997 at Key Solutions, Otley, UK"
      desc="Research Machines is a key player in the educational software market and at Otley we develped  the Integris system of school management systems. A multiplatform system that includes both school and Local Authority software. In addition to this I was influential in developing pupil assesment and curriculum solutions for both the UK and Western Australia. A wide spread of technology was in use far too extensive to fully document in such a fast changing scene as software development but to include MS SQL Server, VB, C#, VBA, Xml, Json, Java and Javascript."
    />
