      title="Now it starts to get complicated! Sub Contract Panel Beater Paint Sprayer."
      subtitle="From 1983 to 1995 at GB Autos Staincliffe & others, UK"
      desc="Accident repair, and repaints on cars and light commercial vehicles. With a smattering of classic vehicle restoration."
