      title="Prior to this self employment as a mechanic and panel beater."
      subtitle="From 1972 to 1983 at Various locations"
      desc="Covering a whole swathe of time as a painter / panel beater and mechanic. Mainly self employed but with long stretches of employment as foreman or chargehand at dealer franchise's. Even including a period as a workshop manager in Johanasburg SA."
    />
