      title="Motor Vehicle development and design."
      subtitle="From 1961 to 1972 at various locations"
      desc="Consolidating a whole lot of creative work developing and producing racing and road going cars, both on my own account and for Sarcon at Yeadon Leeds. Skills at this period were in GRP, welding painting and even a little aero work."
    />
